#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:48 dc16a947c34c4d858779b2b216272a14
msgid "使用PlyPlusKit 工具擦除开发板已经烧录的固件，RST和PROG按键同时按下："
msgstr "Use the PlyPlusKit tool to erase the firmware already flashed on the development board. Press and hold the RST and PROG buttons at the same time:"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:52 807653b572634171a71546bc3741fdcf
msgid "出现UART RX : cmd>>:信息，则表示进入了烧录模式，点击Erase,擦除成功如图："
msgstr "When the message \"UART RX : cmd>>:\" appears, it indicates that the board has entered flashing mode. Click \"Erase\". A successful erase is shown below:"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:56 b54239a02fb041c784f0ae003116c474
msgid "从浏览器的 SDK 安装目录下的example\\ble_peripheral选择一个样例，比如 bleUart-RawPass，打开MDK 项目文件。"
