msgstr "Compile the project using KEIL to generate the HEX file."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:65 7b2e1e0251934a749edaec91fd77f2d0
msgid "3. 调试和烧写"
msgstr "3. Debugging and Flashing"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:67 38a6efad23ba40208a1cedd3b473d853
msgid "在MDK工具栏按钮，点击 Option for target 按钮 ，打开项目的 option 对话框。"
msgstr "In the MDK toolbar, click the \"Option for target\" button to open the project \"option\" dialog box."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:71 86b37f79a72445bca107f4415f393b35
msgid "在 C/C++标签页的 Preprocessor SymbolsDefine 里面，开发者可以改变对应的预编译宏："
msgstr "In the C/C++ tab, under \"Preprocessor Symbols -> Define\", developers can change the corresponding precompiled macros:"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:73 4ec811278ab74a818a2be55d0a492670
msgid "CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MODE_SLEEP ：使能低功耗模式，固件程序执行过程中， 会在空闲过程进入睡眠，睡眠之后调试器无法进行调试跟踪，断点也失效。"
msgstr "CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MODE_SLEEP: Enables low-power mode. During firmware execution, the device enters sleep mode when idle. After entering sleep mode, the debugger cannot perform debugging or tracing, and breakpoints become invalid."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:74 077de89d43054432877a4b8c9b058001
msgid "CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MOD_ENO_SLEEP ：关闭低功耗模式，固件程序执行过 程中，处理器一直处于唤醒状态。"
msgstr "CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MOD_ENO_SLEEP: Disables low-power mode. During firmware execution, the processor remains awake."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:75 312ae3e53ffd4469b98ebe76133c048c
msgid "DEBUG_INFO=1：使能调试信息，默认通过串口输出：P9(Tx),P10(Rx)"
msgstr "DEBUG_INFO=1: Enables debug information output. By default, debug information is output through the serial port: P9 (Tx), P10 (Rx)."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:76 a0df89012a6d4c8bae5bc3962b637dcd
msgid "DEBUG_INFO=0：关闭调试信息"
msgstr "DEBUG_INFO=0: Disables debug information output."

